girl\u2019: Yvette Monreal & Christopher James Baker Set As Regulars In DC Universe Series|last=Petski|first=Denise|work=[[Deadline Hollywood]]|date=November 29, 2018|accessdate=November 29, 2018|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181130122521/https://deadline.com/2018/11/stargirl-yvette-monreal-christopher-james-baker-set-as-regulars-in-dc-universe-series-1202510976/|archive-date=November 30, 2018|url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"McHale\">{{cite web|url=https://variety.com/2018/tv/news/joel-mchale-starman-dc-universe-stargirl-exclusive-1203087415/|title=Joel McHale Cast as Starman in DC Universe\u2019s \u2018Stargirl\u2019 (EXCLUSIVE)|last=Turchiano|first=Danielle|work=[[Variety (magazine)|Variety]]|date=December 12, 2018|accessdate=January 13, 2019|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181215224818/https://variety.com/2018/tv/news/joel-mchale-starman-dc-universe-stargirl-exclusive-1203087415/|archive-date=December 15, 2018|url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"Ferrigno\">{{cite web|url=https://tvline.com/2018/12/13/stargirl-casts-hourman-lou-ferrigno-jr-dc-universe/|title=Stargirl Casts Lou Ferrigno Jr. as Hourman, Founding Member of JSA|last=Mitovitch|first=Matt Webb|work=[[TV Line]]|date=December 13, 2018|accessdate=January 13, 2019|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190104022117/https://tvline.com/2018/12/13/stargirl-casts-hourman-lou-ferrigno-jr-dc-universe/|archive-date=January 4, 2019|url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"Stapf\">{{cite web|url=https://www.tvinsider.com/738208/dc-universe-stargirl-wildcat-brian-stapf/|title=DC Universe's 'Stargirl' Casts Brian Stapf as Wildcat|last=Holbrook|first=Damian|work=[[TV Insider]]|date=December 13, 2018|accessdate=January 13, 2019|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181221041306/https://www.tvinsider.com/738208/dc-universe-stargirl-wildcat-brian-stapf/|archive-date=December 21, 2018|url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"Thomas\">{{cite web|url=https://ew.com/tv/2018/12/17/stargirl-he