and-2-jumanji-3-stargirl-plus-pilot-season/|title=What\u2019s filming in Atlanta now? Bad Boys 3, Zombieland 2, Jumanji 3, Stargirl, plus pilot season|last=Walljaspter|first=Matt|work=[[Atlanta (magazine)|Atlanta]]|date=March 29, 2019|accessdate=April 3, 2020|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190401042713/https://www.atlantamagazine.com/news-culture-articles/whats-filming-in-atlanta-now-bad-boys-3-zombieland-2-jumanji-3-stargirl-plus-pilot-season/|archive-date=April 1, 2019|url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"Khan\">{{cite web |url=https://deadline.com/2019/04/castle-rock-cast-john-hoogenakker-stargirl-hina-khan-1202597383/ |title='Castle Rock' Casts John Hoogenakker; 'Stargirl' Adds Hina Khan |work=[[Deadline Hollywood]] |first=Denise |last=Petski |date=April 17, 2019 |accessdate=April 17, 2019 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190417222007/https://deadline.com/2019/04/castle-rock-cast-john-hoogenakker-stargirl-hina-khan-1202597383/ |archive-date=April 17, 2019 |url-status=live }}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"AtlantaFilming2\">{{cite web|url=https://www.atlantamagazine.com/news-culture-articles/whats-filming-in-atlanta-now-irresistible-hbos-watchmen-the-outsider-stargirl-fear-street-and-more/|title=What\u2019s filming in Atlanta now? Irresistible, HBO\u2019s Watchmen, The Outsider, Stargirl, Fear Street, and more|last=Walljaspter|first=Matt|work=[[Atlanta (magazine)|Atlanta]]|date=April 30, 2019|accessdate=April 3, 2020|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190430235801/https://www.atlantamagazine.com/news-culture-articles/whats-filming-in-atlanta-now-irresistible-hbos-watchmen-the-outsider-stargirl-fear-street-and-more/|archive-date=April 30, 2019|url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"Toprak\">{{cite web|url=https://filmmusicreporter.com/2019/06/25/pinar-toprak-to-score-dc-universes-stargirl/|title=Pinar Toprak to Score DC Universe\u2019s \u2018Stargirl\u2019|work=Film Music Reporter|date=June 25, 2019|accessdate=April 3, 2020|archive-url=https://